’Щ@39a3f882c65febfbb56df7984b8b09bb13839d9fd235491374a645d6fea6d3e1ЪЊTitle: title: bits or
Path: Examples
Content:
Apply bits or to two numbers
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 2 | bits or 6
6

```
Apply bitwise or to a list of numbers
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [8 3 2] | bits or 2
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ 0 в”‚ 10 в”‚
в”‚ 1 в”‚  3 в”‚
в”‚ 2 в”‚  2 в”‚
в•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї


```
Apply bitwise or to binary data
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[88 cc] | bits or 0x[42 32]
Length: 2 (0x2) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ca fe                                                Г—Г—


```
Apply bitwise or to binary data of varying lengths with specified endianness
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[c0 ff ee] | bits or 0x[ff] --endian big
Length: 3 (0x3) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   c0 ff ff                                             Г—Г—Г—


```
Apply bitwise or to input binary data smaller than the operor
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[ff] | bits or 0x[12 34 56] --endian little
Length: 3 (0x3) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ff 34 56                                             Г—4V


```
